data.description: 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in a highly sought-after area close to the University of Southern California (USC). New roof and new solar installed. Main floor welcomes you with a warm and inviting living room, perfect for relaxing or entertaining guests. Adjacent to the living room, you'll find a formal dining room. The kitchen is practical and open. Additionally, there is a 3/4 bath on the main floor for added connivence. Laundry room is also located downstairs. An additional feature of the home is an office/bonus room that can serve as a dedicated workspace, study area, or even a playroom, depending on your needs. There's also a room with a functional hot tub that has proper venting, providing a relaxing escape right within your own home. Upper level of the house are three well-appointed bedrooms, each offering its own unique charm and comfort. There is also a full bathroom on this floor. You can step out onto the balcony to enjoy some fresh air and take in the neighborhood views. There is extra living quarters in the rear yard, unknown if permitted, but occupied. The backyard of the property is gated, offering privacy and security. In addition, there is secured alley access to the rear yard. This feature is particularly valuable in a busy urban area like this one.
